    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"hi1t0"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"be86443b-54a1-5094-b18d-d6946bcd12ff","fields":{"slug":"/20220303/"},"excerpt":"環境 MacOS 11.5.2 VSCode 1.64.2 画像表示  または  今回の場合同じディレクトリに画像と markdown ファイルがある \nとすると以下のように表示される\n 画像のサイズを変更したい場合  のように width を指定することで変更できる Gatsby のブログ markdown…","html":"<h4 id=\"環境\">環境</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>MacOS 11.5.2</li>\n<li>VSCode 1.64.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"画像表示\">画像表示</h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">![画像表示不可時テキスト](/path/to/画像)</code></p>\n<p>または</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src=\"/path/to/画像\" alt=\"画像表示不可時テキスト\"></code></p>\n<p>今回の場合同じディレクトリに画像と markdown ファイルがある</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">![test](1.png)</code>\nとすると以下のように表示される\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/c26ae/1.png 158w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/6bdcf/1.png 315w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png 630w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/40601/1.png 945w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png 1228w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>画像のサイズを変更したい場合</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src=\"1.png\" alt=\"テスト\" width=\"50%\"></code></p>\n<p>のように width を指定することで変更できる</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"テスト\" title=\"テスト\" src=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png\" srcset=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/c26ae/1.png 158w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/6bdcf/1.png 315w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png 630w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/40601/1.png 945w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png 1228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br>\n<p>Gatsby のブログ markdown をブラウザ表示させる時は、このままではサイズが変更されない。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>test<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>png<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>このように表記することでサイズ変更できる</p>\n<div style=\"width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto\">\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/c26ae/1.png 158w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/6bdcf/1.png 315w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png 630w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/40601/1.png 945w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png 1228w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</div>\n<h4 id=\"プレビュー表示\">プレビュー表示</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>shift + command + p</li>\n<li>検索欄に markdown</li>\n<li>検索結果の Markdown: Open Preview to the Side を選択</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/c26ae/1.png 158w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/6bdcf/1.png 315w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/f058b/1.png 630w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/40601/1.png 945w,\n/static/35fafcf7248ab200b1f9e0d38a8e5717/5148a/1.png 1228w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/56caf/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.51898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/f058b/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/c26ae/2.png 158w,\n/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/6bdcf/2.png 315w,\n/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/f058b/2.png 630w,\n/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/40601/2.png 945w,\n/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/78612/2.png 1260w,\n/static/e564a8c7df622a7d56e26d74b00cc01a/56caf/2.png 1712w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>又は、ショートカットキー command + k, v で表示</p>\n<h4 id=\"拡張機能を入れる\">拡張機能を入れる</h4>\n<p>VSCode で markdown を書く時に便利な拡張機能</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Markdown All in One</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>markdownlint</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>拡張機能を入れるには</p>\n<ol>\n<li>shift + command + p</li>\n<li>検索欄に extensions と入力</li>\n<li>Install Extensions を選択</li>\n<li>左の検索欄で markdown と検索</li>\n<li>表示されたものの中から Markdown All in One と markdownlint をインストールする</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/c929c/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/f058b/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/c26ae/3.png 158w,\n/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/6bdcf/3.png 315w,\n/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/f058b/3.png 630w,\n/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/40601/3.png 945w,\n/static/3e580b8a48698d70fd4188aef7b78fed/c929c/3.png 1218w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div style=\"width: 40%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto\">\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 518px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a206ca2e9edab9ec767727bef83a5460/6b9fd/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 192.40506329113924%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/a206ca2e9edab9ec767727bef83a5460/6b9fd/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a206ca2e9edab9ec767727bef83a5460/c26ae/4.png 158w,\n/static/a206ca2e9edab9ec767727bef83a5460/6bdcf/4.png 315w,\n/static/a206ca2e9edab9ec767727bef83a5460/6b9fd/4.png 518w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</div>\n<p>Markdown All in One を入れると便利なショートカットキー、見出しのナンバリング、リスト・リンクの入力支援などが使えるようになる</p>\n<p>例えば、url を command + c でコピーしておき、リンクを貼り付けたいワードを選択し、command + v をすると自動でリンクの形式にしてくれる</p>\n<p>markdownlint は構文とスタイルをチェックしてくれる拡張機能</p>\n<div style=\"width: 80%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto\">\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/21537276ce661bf29fa879d7a4aaf7e7/914ae/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test\"\n        title=\"test\"\n        src=\"/static/21537276ce661bf29fa879d7a4aaf7e7/f058b/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/21537276ce661bf29fa879d7a4aaf7e7/c26ae/5.png 158w,\n/static/21537276ce661bf29fa879d7a4aaf7e7/6bdcf/5.png 315w,\n/static/21537276ce661bf29fa879d7a4aaf7e7/f058b/5.png 630w,\n/static/21537276ce661bf29fa879d7a4aaf7e7/914ae/5.png 860w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</div>\n<p>画像のように波線表示がされるようになります。ここが、Markdown の構文的にまたはスタイル的に修正したほうがよい箇所という具合になる</p>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"https://maasaablog.com/tools/visual-studio-code/1762/\">VsCode でマークダウンファイル(.md)を快適に使用する Tips</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"VSCodeでMarkdownを書く時に知るべきこと","date":"March 03, 2022","description":null,"tags":["markdown","tips"]},"tableOfContents":""},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/new-beginnings/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"New Beginnings"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/20220304/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Github Actionsでnpm ciがうまく通らなかった"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"be86443b-54a1-5094-b18d-d6946bcd12ff","previousPostId":"aee1dbd1-5550-5812-b9a1-3e4214895be1","nextPostId":"3820e968-0f5d-54ac-a3d7-17dd220abb8e"}},
